517
00:33:18,498 --> 00:33:21,376
GRACE:
Get your things.

518
00:33:21,542 --> 00:33:24,003
Balaclava.

519
00:33:27,465 --> 00:33:29,217
Easy, easy.

520
00:33:30,385 --> 00:33:34,972
