00:35:51,108 --> 00:35:54,403
Mind Brussels sprouts.

544
00:35:58,324 --> 00:36:00,117
This way.

545
00:36:08,709 --> 00:36:12,255
- Parachute silk.
- Parachute silk.

546
00:36:12,797 --> 00:36:14,799
WOMAN 2:
Parachute silk!

