552
00:36:47,957 --> 00:36:52,587
Don't be so sure. When I jitterbug....

553
00:36:54,422 --> 00:36:56,424
[BIG BAND PLAYING]

554
00:36:58,593 --> 00:37:00,177
[SQUEALING]

555
00:37:27,371 --> 00:37:28,623
